<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<title>BookWithUs</title>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<!-- @import "header.kit" -->
		<section class="why">
			<img class = 'why__bg' src="img/why/mont_bg.jpg" alt="">
			<img class = 'why__mont' src="img/why/mont.png" alt="">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="why__wrap">
					<h1 class="why__title">Why <br>
					LuxTrips</h1>
				</div>
				<div class="why__advantages">
					<div class="why__row">
						<div class="why__column">
							<div class="why__item why__item-l">
								<div class="why__img">
									<div class="why__img-wrap">
										<img src="img/why/adv-1.jpg" alt="">
									</div>
								</div>
								<div   class="why__info-text">
									<div data-da="why-client__mobile,2,991.98" class="why__adv-title">Bespoke experience of travelling</div>
									<p data-da="why-client__mobile,3,991.98" class="why__text">Being expert Luxury Travel Designers, Lux Trips offers bespoke experience of travelling. </p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="why__column">
							<div class="why__item why__item-c">
								<div class="why__img"><img src="img/why/adv-2.jpg" alt=""></div>
								<div class="why__info-text">
									<div data-da="why-client__mobile,1,991.98" class="why__adv-title">Collecting precious moments is our utmost goal.</div>
									<p data-da="why-client__mobile,last,991.98" class="why__text">Our exclusive network of trusted local partners allows us to carefully curate every detail.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="why__column">
							<div class="why__item why__item-r">
								<div class="why__img"><img src="img/why/adv-3.jpg" alt=""></div>
								<div class="why__info-text">
									<div  data-da="why-client__mobile,4,991.98" class="why__adv-title">We personalize each trip</div>
									<p  data-da="why-client__mobile,5,991.98" class="why__text">Thanks to our extensive knowledge and operation in the industry, we personalize each trip according to the needs and wishes of our clients.  </p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="why-client">
			<div class="why-client__decor-1">
				<img src="img/why/decor-1.png" alt="">
			</div>
			<div class="why-client__decor-2">
				<img src="img/why/decor-2.png" alt="">
			</div>
			<div class="why-client__decor-3">
				<img src="img/why/decor-3.png" alt="">
			</div>
			<div class="why-client__decor-4">
				<img src="img/why/decor-4.png" alt="">
			</div>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="why-client__mobile"></div>
				<div class="why-client__row-text">
					<div class="why-client__column-text">
						<h3 class="why-client__mintitle">Creating a unique experience for each client </h3>
					</div>
					<div class="why-client__column-text">
						<p class="why-client__mintext">Starting from suggesting destinations to visit in the current season, to the selection of the most exquisite locations for a special event or a family dinner. </p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="why-client__stat stat-why-client">
					<div class="stat-why-client__row">
						<div class="stat-why-client__column">
							<div class="stat-why-client__item">
								<div class="stat-why-client__romb">
									<img src="img/big-romb.svg" alt="">
									<div class="stat-why-client__info">
										<span class="stat-why-client__number">985</span>
										<span class="stat-why-client__text">Luxury trips provided</span>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="stat-why-client__column">
							<div class="stat-why-client__item">
								<div class="stat-why-client__romb">
									<img src="img/big-romb.svg" alt="">
									<div class="stat-why-client__info">
										<span class="stat-why-client__number">68</span>
										<span class="stat-why-client__text">Destinations</span>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="stat-why-client__column">
							<div class="stat-why-client__item">
								<div class="stat-why-client__romb">
									<img src="img/big-romb.svg" alt="">
									<div class="stat-why-client__info">
										<span class="stat-why-client__number">812</span>
										<span class="stat-why-client__text">Happy Customers</span>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="why-client__packages packages-why-client">
				<h3 class="packages-why-client__title">In Lux Trips we plan, organize and manage tailor-made itineraries for our clients.</h3>
				<p class="packages-why-client__text">Offering exclusive tours, exceptional accommodations and personalized journey-planning.</p>
				<div class="bg-wrap">
					<img class = 'bg' src="img/why/bg_why-sum.jpg" alt="">
					<div class="container">
						<div class="packages-why-client__row">
							<div class="packages-why-client__column">
								<div class="packages-why-client__img">
									<div class="packages-why-client__wrap-img">
										<img src="img/why/pack-1.jpg" alt="">
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="packages-why-client__column">
								<p class="packages-why-client__text">We provide our clients with access to exclusive events and experiences, such as glamping or fishing on private islands, private vineyard wine-tasting and tours, or cruising a sea with a flock of dolphins, to name just a few.</p>
								<p class="packages-why-client__text">Our location scouting for events and holidays encompasses diverse types of villas and chalets, luxury resorts and world-class hotels around the world. </p>
								<div class="packages-why-client__button packages-why-client__button-h">
									<button class="packages-why-client__btn btn">Luxury packages</button>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="packages-why-client__button packages-why-client__button-m">
							<button class="packages-why-client__btn btn">Luxury packages</button>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="why-client__customize cutsomize-why-client">
						<div class="container">
							<div class="cutsomize-why-client__title">We customize your journey by selecting the most convenient travelling options, including private yachts, jets, charter flights and supercars.</div>
						</div>
						<div class="cutsomize-why-client__slider">
							<div class="cutsomize-why-client__slide">
								<div class="cutsomize-why-client__img" style="background:url(img/bookUs/i_01.jpg) no-repeat;">
									<div class="cutsomize-why-client__name"><span>Supercars</span></div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="cutsomize-why-client__slide">
								<div class="cutsomize-why-client__img" style="background:url(img/bookUs/i_02.jpg) no-repeat;">
									<div class="cutsomize-why-client__name"><span>Hotels</span></div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="cutsomize-why-client__slide">
								<div class="cutsomize-why-client__img" style="background:url(img/bookUs/i_02.jpg) no-repeat;">
									<div class="cutsomize-why-client__name"><span>Hotels</span></div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="cutsomize-why-client__slide">
								<div class="cutsomize-why-client__img" style="background:url(img/bookUs/i_02.jpg) no-repeat;">
									<div class="cutsomize-why-client__name"><span>Hotels</span></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="container">
							<div class="cutsomize-why-client__wrap">
								<button class="cutsomize-why-client__btn btn">Book now</button>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="why-client__contact contact-why-client">
				<div class="container">
					<p class="contact-why-client__text">As a Luxury Travel Designer, we make it our mission to transform clientsâ€™ interests and dreams into one-of-a-kind travel experience through the provision of premium quality services.</p>
					<div class="contact-why-client__title">Importantly, in Lux Trips we get to know our clients personally, and hence, we get to have a relationship with each of them.</div>
					<p class="contact-why-client__text">We construct long-lasting connections thanks to the unforgettable trips we design, as we believe that travel is all about feelings, and memories are the most precious gifts we want our customer to bring back with them.
					</p>
					<div class="cutsomize-why-client__wrap">
						<button class="cutsomize-why-client__btn btn">Contact us</button>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="contact-why-client__img">
					<img src="img/why/bg-why-girl.jpg" alt="">
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="packages__footer footer-packages">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="footer-packages__dec">
						<div class="footer-packages__item" style="background:url(img/packages/footer-img.jpg) no-repeat;">
							<h3 class="footer-packages__title">Get weekly inspiration and expert advice</h3>
							<div class="footer-packages__suptitle">Sign up for our Weekly Newsletter</div>
							<div class="footer-packages__form">
								<form>
									<div class="footer-packages__main">
										<input placeholder = 'Email address' type="text">
										<div class="footer-packages__wrap">
											<button class="footer-packages__btn btn">Subscribe</button>
										</div>
									</div>
								</form>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
